Contrary to TFS title, "(Stored on 1 Petabyte of SSDs)" is not "used 36 Solidigm SSD" (which hold a petabyte of data).  One petabyte of SSDs would (probably) fill a few Library of Congresses -- in which case that unit could simply be used.<nobr> <wbr></nobr>:-)</p></div>
	</div>

